@nowaistallowed has me feeling amazing at just 1 month postpartum with their shape wear products💗. as you all know the SnapBack can be difficult but I have already made progress going down to my third latch. @nowaistallowed has helped me kick start my fine ass mom journey and I’m not going to lie yall I have a whole collection! ☺️❤️They literally have everything from everyday shape wear to post op products. 

USE CODE “TAINA” for $$ OFF!!
